{"id": 7333, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "HL", "paper": "3", "year": "2017", "session": "17N", "subtopic": "d-8-nuclear-medicine, d-6-environmental-impact-of-some-medications", "title": "17N.3.HL.TZ0.21", "topic_id": "d", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"specification\">\n<p>Lutetium-177 is used in radiotherapy. It emits beta radiation when it decays.</p>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p>State a nuclear equation to show the decay of lutetium-177.</p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[2]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p>The half-life of lutetium-177 is 6.73 days. Determine the percentage of a sample of lutetium-177 remaining after 14.0 days.</p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[2]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p>Explain the low environmental impact of most medical nuclear waste.</p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[2]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">c.</div>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"{}_{71}^{177}{\\text{Lu}} \\to {}_{71}^{177}{\\text{Hf}} + {}_{ - 1}^0{\\text{e}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<msubsup>\n<mrow>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>71</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>177</mn>\n</mrow>\n</msubsup>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>Lu</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mo stretchy=\"false\">→</mo>\n<msubsup>\n<mrow>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>71</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>177</mn>\n</mrow>\n</msubsup>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>Hf</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mo>+</mo>\n<msubsup>\n<mrow>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mo>−</mo>\n<mn>1</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mn>0</mn>\n</msubsup>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>e</mtext>\n</mrow>\n</math></span> «+ <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\nu \" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mi>ν</mi>\n</math></span>»</p>\n<p>Hf</p>\n<p>correct <em>A</em> and <em>Z</em> <em><strong>AND</strong> </em>beta product</p>\n<p><em>Accept “β/ β<sup>–</sup>/e/e<sup>–</sup>” for “<span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"{}_{-1}^{~0}{\\text{e}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<msubsup>\n<mrow>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mo>−</mo>\n<mn>1</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext> </mtext>\n<mn>0</mn>\n</mrow>\n</msubsup>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>e</mtext>\n</mrow>\n</math></span>”.</em></p>\n<p><em>Accept “<sup>177</sup>Lu → <sup>177</sup>Hf + e<sup>–</sup> «+ <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\nu \" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mi>ν</mi>\n</math></span>»”.</em></p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p>number of half-lives = <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{t}{{{t_{^{\\frac{1}{2}}}}}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mi>t</mi>\n<mrow>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mi>t</mi>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi></mi>\n<mrow>\n<mfrac>\n<mn>1</mn>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</mfrac>\n</mrow>\n</msup>\n</mrow>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</math></span> = 2.08</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{N\\left( t \\right)}}{{{N_0}}} = {0.5^{\\frac{{14.0}}{{6.73}}}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mi>N</mi>\n<mrow>\n<mo>(</mo>\n<mi>t</mi>\n<mo>)</mo>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mi>N</mi>\n<mn>0</mn>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mn>0.5</mn>\n<mrow>\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mn>14.0</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>6.73</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</mrow>\n</msup>\n</mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\lambda  = \" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mi>λ</mi>\n<mo>=</mo>\n</math></span> «<span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{{\\text{ln}}2}}{{{t_{^{\\frac{1}{2}}}}}} = \\frac{{{\\text{ln}}2}}{{6.73}} = \" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>ln</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mi>t</mi>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi></mi>\n<mrow>\n<mfrac>\n<mn>1</mn>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</mfrac>\n</mrow>\n</msup>\n</mrow>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>ln</mtext>\n</mrow>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>6.73</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n<mo>=</mo>\n</math></span>» 0.103 «day<sup>–1</sup>»</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{N\\left( t \\right)}}{{{N_0}}} = {e^{ - 0.103\\, \\times 14.0}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mi>N</mi>\n<mrow>\n<mo>(</mo>\n<mi>t</mi>\n<mo>)</mo>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mrow>\n<msub>\n<mi>N</mi>\n<mn>0</mn>\n</msub>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi>e</mi>\n<mrow>\n<mo>−</mo>\n<mn>0.103</mn>\n<mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>14.0</mn>\n</mrow>\n</msup>\n</mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>23.6 «%»</p>\n<p><em>Award<strong> [2]</strong> for correct final answer.</em></p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p><em>Any two of:</em></p>\n<p>emits weak ionising radiation</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p>low activity/radioactivity</p>\n<p>can be stored until material becomes inactive <em><strong>AND</strong> </em>then disposed with normal waste</p>\n<p>«isotopes» have short lives</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p>exist for a short period of time</p>\n<p><em>Award <strong>[1 max]</strong> for “low-level waste/LLW”.</em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[Max 2 Marks]</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">c.</div>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n[N/A]\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n[N/A]\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n[N/A]\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">c.</div>\n</div>"}